   January 30, 2002         DOL > Secretary Chao's Page

   Secretary of Labor Elaine L. Chao

   Secretary of Labor Elaine L. Chao
   "To succeed in the 21st Century, our nation must be prepared to adapt
   to changes in our economy - in how we work, where we work, and how we
   balance our professional and family lives."

                                        -Secretary of Labor Elaine L. Chao


